[b]Basic Movment tut[/b]
[i]In this tut you will hopefully learn the basics of space invaider movement (warning this is bad actionscript movment) ;)[/i]

[b]Step 1:[/b][i]open up a new Flash Document and Make a Circle in the middle of it.[/i]
[b]Step 2:[/b][i]right click the circle and select "Convert to symbol" then select button and call it ummm well anything you want.[/i]
[b]Step 3:[/b][i]click the circle and at the bottom click the arrrow that is facing up and in the actionscript bit add this.[/i]
[code]
on(keyPress "<left>"){

this._x -= 5

}
on(keyPress "<right>"){

this._x += 5

}
on(keyPress "<up>"){

	this._y-= 5

}
on(KeyPress "<down>"){

	this._Y+= 5

}[/code]
[b]Step 4:[/b][i]now press CTRL + ALT + ENTER and well press the right and left arrow keys.[/i]

